Text: FW Jeffrey K SkillingOriginal Message From Temica Lacy Sent Monday March AM To Fernando Parra Cc Shelly Lambert Subject RE Jeffrey K Skilling Have received the items listed below Okay for Mr Skilling to pay Thomsen Thanks Original Message From Temica Lacy Sent Monday March AM To Fernando Parra Cc Shelly Lambert Subject Jeffrey K Skilling Have received a draw request and the following is needed Borrowers signature is missing on Draw Request Form Borrowers signature is missing on Contractors Disbursement Disclosure Form Inspection will be ordered Thanks Temica Lacy ext CONFIDENTIALITY NOTICE The information contained in this ELECTRONIC MAIL transmission is confidential It may also be privileged work product or proprietary information This information is intended for the exclusive use of the addressees If you are not the intended recipient you are hereby notified that any use disclosure dissemination distribution other than to the addressees copying or taking of any action because of this information is strictly prohibited

FW Jeff Skilling Loan It seems everything on our end checks out Original Message From Irene Hargy Sent Monday March PM To Fernando Parra Cc Shelly Lambert Subject Jeff Skilling Loan Have received the architects signature on the above however we still need the following items Borrowers signature on the page draw request and the Contractors Disbursement Disclosure and change order We were also advising on the last application because he is now holding only retainage he would be providing us with an all bill paid affidavit with each draw request Please forward Thanks Irene Hargy Ext CONFIDENTIALITY NOTICE The information contained in this ELECTRONIC MAIL transmission is confidential It may also be privileged work product or proprietary information This information is intended for the exclusive use of the addressees If you are not the intended recipient you are hereby notified that any use disclosure dissemination distribution other than to the addressees copying or taking of any action because of this information is strictly prohibited

FW Jeff skilling Loan Below are the comments from our inspector regarding the current draw in the amount of M It may be that some of the hardware is off site and hasnt been installed as of the inspection date Im sure Jeff can address this Call if any questions Original Message From Irene Hargy Sent Monday November AM To Fernando Parra Cc Shelly Lambert Subject Jeff skilling Loan Have received inspection on the above and have noted the following Interior hardware installed line item drawing Only completed drawer glides and door hinges are all that is done We are also still waiting for the signatures on the page draw the Contractors Disbursement Disclosure and change order Thanks Irene Hargy ext CONFIDENTIALITY NOTICE The information contained in this ELECTRONIC MAIL transmission is confidential It may also be privileged work product or proprietary information This information is intended for the exclusive use of the addressees If you are not the intended recipient you are hereby notified that any use disclosure dissemination distribution other than to the addressees copying or taking of any action because of this information is strictly prohibited

FW Skilling Jeff FYI Original Message From Albert Ibanez Sent Thursday October AM To Fernando Parra Brandy Akers Subject FW Skilling Have received inspection report and the following was noted Fencing is not all the way to the street stops at bushes No credit Original Message From Albert Ibanez Sent Thursday October AM To Fernando Parra Brandy Akers Cc Patti McNeil Temica Lacy Subject Skilling Have received a Draw request and the following is needed to process Borrower signature on Draw Request Form Borrower signature on Contract Disbursement All bill paid Affidavit if last draw per customers Attorney An Affidavit of Completion Signed by Borrower Inspection will be ordered Thank you Albert Ibanez Real Estate Service Group Fax CONFIDENTIALITY NOTICE The information contained in this ELECTRONIC MAIL transmission is confidential It may also be privileged work product or proprietary information This information is intended for the exclusive use of the addressees If you are not the intended recipient you are hereby notified that any use disclosure dissemination distribution other than to the addressees copying or taking of any action because of this information is strictly prohibited

FW Jeff Skillingjeff I presume this email address is still good It appears it is Ok to pay this draw By the way are there any more draws Original Message From Patti McNeil Sent Thursday August PM To Fernando Parra Brandy Akers Subject Jeff Skilling We have received all the signed documentation for application no It is okay to release payment to Jeff Thomsen Thanks Patti McNeill RE Construction Funding Mgr Fax CONFIDENTIALITY NOTICE The information contained in this ELECTRONIC MAIL transmission is confidential It may also be privileged work product or proprietary information This information is intended for the exclusive use of the addressees If you are not the intended recipient you are hereby notified that any use disclosure dissemination distribution other than to the addressees copying or taking of any action because of this information is strictly prohibited

FW Jeffrey SkillingJeff info on the latest draw Everything seems Ok with the exception of some unsigned forms by you or your representative as well as the revised draw request Original Message From Temica Lacy Sent Friday July AM To Fernando Parra Cc Shelly Lambert Subject RE Jeffrey Skilling Please note we have received a revised draw request that includes Change Order iao and the borrower signature is missing Thanks Original Message From Temica Lacy Sent Tuesday July AM To Fernando Parra Cc Shelly Lambert Subject Jeffrey Skilling Have received a draw request and the following is needed to process Architect needs to certify the G Application for Payment Borrower needs to sign the Draw Request Form Borrower needs to sign the Contractor Disbursement Disclosure Change Order for Inspection will be ordered Thanks Temica T Lacy Southwest Bank of Texas Real Estate Processor CONFIDENTIALITY NOTICE The information contained in this ELECTRONIC MAIL transmission is confidential It may also be privileged work product or proprietary information This information is intended for the exclusive use of the addressees If you are not the intended recipient you are hereby notified that any use disclosure dissemination distribution other than to the addressees copying or taking of any action because of this information is strictly prohibited
